Managing women of childbearing age with chronic myeloid leukemia: safety and 
treatment considerations.

Robertson HF(1)(2), Buckton MJ(1)(2), Apperley JF(1)(2).

Author information:
(1)Centre for Haematology, Imperial College London, London, UK.
(2)Department of Clinical Haematology, Hammersmith Hospital, Imperial College 
